  "body": "To make our codebase consistent, should we use arrow functions in tests when it's not necessary to access `this`?\r\n\r\nYES: Respond :+1: \r\n```ts\r\nit(\"example\", () => {\r\n  ...\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\nNO: Respond :-1: \r\n```ts\r\nit(\"example\", function () {\r\n  ...\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nRef: https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/classes.html#public-by-default",
